Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle continues to rage\nagainst the Band of Seven{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who are hell-bent on\navenging Ginkotsu's death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Renkotsu tries to steal the\NSacred Jewel shards from Koga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who has sustained serious injuries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time\nfor a Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All {\i1}right....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should have mounted\nthis on him as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wha....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it, I can't {\i1}move....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do with\NGinkotsu's Sacred Jewel shard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I carry it around\nlike this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Bankotsu will\njust take it from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way I'm letting that\nhappen! Not for that brat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wound is healing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dying won't do anybody\nany good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Ginkotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about\nreporting to Bankotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got one more job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:50.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear to you, I'm going to\nsteal Koga's jewel shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were unconscious\nall night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga? Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were caught in the explosion of\nthat iron monster, Ginkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:24.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow....{\i0} Jeez! I stink\nto high heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How come?! My whole body\njust reeks of dog!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's because Inuyasha\ncarried you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome asked him to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you two let\nhim do that to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two should've carried me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you see, we {\i1}also....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were hurt {\i1}some....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? I told you we should\nhave left him where he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, I never actually expected\nhim to show me any gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to you,\NInuyasha?! You're soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:04.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you guess? I had to wash\noff that stink of wolf on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Makes me sick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Simmer down, {\i1}Koga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm outta here, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I carried him to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now it's no business of ours\nif he lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!\NDon't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You! You're always\nchastising me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you never say a word to\nthat thankless Koga there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sick of your whining about\nthat! All right! I'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kagome.\NYou saved my {\i1}life....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be thanking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All you did was carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looks like he's feeling\nall right to me. Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it looks like he\ncan't move {\i1}yet....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, what about\NMiroku and Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! What's going on with those\ntwo who went to Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}probably....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a poison insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get him before he\ngives this place away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakkaku and Ginta? How are\nyou two feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm still a {\i1}bit....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We got hit pretty {\i1}hard....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:36.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I lost the first-aid kit so\NI can't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's enough that you even\nthought of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike Koga, they're\nvery humble...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you smell it, too, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I sense the presence of\na Sacred Jewel shard nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it you smell, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Smells like {\i1}gunpowder....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The river!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:46.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must be the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've poured a lot of oil on the water!\NYou can't escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Renkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, it's too dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}that....!{\i0} I'll kill\nhim this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Don't, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're too badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For that Renkotsu to\nshow up so soon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,means he's really anxious\nfor me to kill {\i1}him....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Inuyasha!\NYou should wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right! The Robe of the Fire\NRat will protect you from fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you two wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't depend on that\ndamned wolf to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep your hands off him, mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's after my jewel shards! I'll\nbe the one to settle with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If your shards fall into his\nhands, we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:17.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But please be careful, Inuyasha!\NThat fiend is using two jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's fewer than Bankotsu had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So! Inuyasha is back already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong? A little\ntoo hot in that hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm coming to get\nyou so just wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In one {\i1}leap....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would I wait for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}cannon....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't dodge this\nin mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Great! Kirara can't\nbe hurt by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Way to go, Kirara! Now\nlet's go get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara! Get above him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I come, Renkotsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And here I go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:27.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kagome! Get inside!\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I get {\i1}them....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph. Looks like they've\nbeen {\i1}incinerated....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take those Sacred Jewel shards,\nif you don't {\i1}mind....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool! No\none's dead in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be grateful, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's because Kagome managed to\ncover you with Inuyasha's robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not crazy about it\nbelonging to that mutt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you think you've\nbested me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet!\NI'll blow you to hell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are fire bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you set one of those off\ninside here, it'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NThere's no turning back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true... I've been using the\nshard that Ginkotsu left{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}without permission and\NBankotsu will kill me for it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm on to you, that you've\nbeen hiding{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Scared Jewel shards\nyou got from that girl, Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't be angry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was going to hand\nthem over to you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My, aren't you cooperative...\NI knew you were a smart one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just don't let it happen again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, I'm going to have those\nshards in your legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no matter what it {\i1}takes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! With those I can battle\nwith Bankotsu and defeat {\i1}him....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no empty threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He means it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't fall for that twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away\nfrom here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't die... as long as\NI have the shards...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only ones to die\nwill be you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do it now, wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:20.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's up again, mutt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take {\i1}this....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyashaaaaaa!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha? {\i1}Inuyasha....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find\nhim {\i1}soon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must've washed up\non the {\i1}riverbank....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...provided the mutt isn't\nin a million {\i1}pieces....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's true! Come on!\NIf that idiot {\i1}hadn't....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:25.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha wasn't even wearing\nthe Robe of the Fire Rat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}even though it's like\narmor to him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:31.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you've made her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't cry, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault! It's\nbecause he let me wear {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Kagome!\NI saw the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He forced it on you even though\nyou really hated to touch {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey?...Ah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, wolf.\NWho hated to touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:51.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My body is built\ndifferently than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And in addition to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,sure enough, that punk Renkotsu\nvalued his life, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the last minute he\nthrew the fire bombs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! That's what I thought\nhe'd do all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They say that idiots\ndon't {\i1}die....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think I'll let you\nget away with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You gonna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Today is the day I'm gonna\nput your lights out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How? With that beat-up\nbody of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:24.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not hurt, are you?\NYou're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I caused\nyou to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really, truly all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:51.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga?\NYou're just walking away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll walk away for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,seeing as how Kagome\nis upset and {\i1}all....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But listen up, mutt.\NDon't think you've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm never giving up on Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you tell that\nyou've lost, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You get all smug just because\nshe hugged you? Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:27.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It gets you, doesn't it!\NYou deserve it! Stupid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow... somehow it's getting\nharder and harder to cry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one calling the other\nstupid is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't cry with\nall this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing in here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sign of demons at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, there is some\nkind of connection
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between Naraku and\nthe Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's a fact that Saint Hakushin\nwas protecting the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he is helping Naraku out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by putting this barrier around\NMt. Hakurei, {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wouldn't be surprised\nif Naraku were around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go on to\nthe top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we go back empty-handed,\nwe'll hear about it from Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to do something\nabout this barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here we are, finally\nalone together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:38.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I can't make a move!\NAt this rate, I'll {\i1}never....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! I failed again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't manage to steal\NKoga's Sacred Jewel shards...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it gets out that I'm using\NGinkotsu's Sacred Jewel shard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then Bankotsu will kill me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do now...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saimyosho....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}Bankotsu....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Renkotsu. I heard\nfrom the bugs {\i1}here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ginkotsu bit the dust, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um....yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:47.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too bad. After all the time you\nspent reconstructing {\i1}him....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But at least you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, who was after\NSesshomaru, is dead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that means that {\i1}finally....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:09.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it's just the three of us:\nyou, me and Jakotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, I guess I'm going to be\ndepending more heavily on {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:17.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This creep Bankotsu isn't aware\nof Ginkotsu's jewel shard...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, anyway, I guess I'm\nstill of some use to him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I got a reprieve this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}path....{\i0}\NIt's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost like someone\ndestroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like this path\nled up to that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Wanna go in?\N- Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}word....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here! Catch this, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're impressive, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It leads deep into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's faint, but\NI sense an evil aura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sango. No doubt about\nit, Naruku is deep inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:20:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn that Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long is he going to keep\nme shut up in this place?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:27.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Kanna.\NBoy, you've got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't emanate any\ndemonic aura
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so you can come and go on\nsacred ground as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I make even\none step outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that annoying barrier will\nwill purify me! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:45.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These two! The monk\nand the Demon {\i1}Slayer....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're long overdue for\na little {\i1}rumble....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a demonic aura\ndeep inside the sacred Mt. Hakurei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:48.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe two lone humans\nactually came in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're brave, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're not getting outta\nhere alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:57.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! If you suck them up,\nthe poison {\i1}will....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If in doing so, my beloved will\nlive longer, I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:04.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Into the Depths of Mt. Hakurei"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.94,0:24:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sango.\NBut you, at least, must live!
